recipes.title: Sushi (Japan)
recipes.method: In a medium bowl, whisk together the flour, baking soda, and salt. Set aside. 2. In a large mixing bowl, cream the butter, granulated sugar, and brown sugar together until light and fluffy.3. Add the eggs, one at a time, followed by the vanilla extract, and mix until well combined.
